CatDescriptText: The Celebrity Cafe, located at 2103 Centre Avenue, has a sign advertising performance of Honey Boy and His Buzzing Bees.  Rothschild's Bakery is located at 2109 Centre Avenue.
TitMainTitle: Children boarding chartered bus number 350, with sign on side inscribed "Follow Your Dollar Tour, United War Fund, The Community Fund" on Centre Avenue in front of the Celebrity Cafe and Rothschild's Bakery
